name: TTHHEE PPAARRTTYY
wikiSummary: "Tthhee Ppaarrttyy" is the fifth single by Justice, as well as the fifth single by Uffie. It was released as a download without the album version, instead containing a remixed Radio Edit and the live version found on A Cross The Universe (spelled with more letters as "Ttthhheee Pppaaarrrtttyyy"). The song contains an uncredited sample from Three 6 Mafia's "Stay Fly" and features vocals by Uffie.
